}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== This model does not appear to have been distributed in the States.
"11340Y20DU00304A1" and "2009/03/06" is silkscreened on the board, implying the device was manufactured by [[AMIT]].
[http://www.hardware.com.br/comunidade/linux-reconhece/1104122/ A mention of an OUI of 1C:AF:F7] and [http://www.reclameaqui.com.br/774168/dlink-brasil/router-150-di-524/ a mention of an OUI of 00:26:5A]
